00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:46.785
Next, we have another string variable called draftMessage.

00:00:46.785 --> 00:00:50.970
The value is, "You have blank email drafts."

00:00:50.970 --> 00:00:53.835
Blank actually refers to a number of draft emails,

00:00:53.835 --> 00:00:55.740
