00:01:06.375 --> 00:01:10.035
There is no Else block of code down here and that's perfectly fine.

00:01:10.035 --> 00:01:15.195
This statement reads, If the number of emails in inbox equals zero,

00:01:15.195 --> 00:01:18.875
then perform the code within these opening and closing braces.

00:01:18.875 --> 00:01:22.905
We remember that numberOfEmailsInInbox is equal to zero,

00:01:22.905 --> 00:01:27.810
so this code in the opening and closing braces would get executed.

00:01:27.810 --> 00:01:31.440
It simply updates the emailMessage variable to say,

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:33.075
"You have no new messages."

00:01:33.075 --> 00:01:37.380
Okay, so we know that the latest value of emailMessage is,

00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:38.730
"You have no new messages",

00:01:38.730 --> 00:01:41.970
